org.dockbox.selene.core.objects.keys

Interface KeyHolder<T extends KeyHolder>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - The type which the Key can modify.
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ArmorStand, Entity<T>, Item, ItemFrame
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractIdentifiable, Player, ReferencedItem, SpongeArmorStand, SpongeEntity, SpongeItem, SpongeItemFrame, SpongePlayer

    public interface KeyHolder<T extends KeyHolder>
    Low-level interface which can be used to access and retrieve values from a implementation of this interface using the Key type. This interface provides default implementations, expecting the implementation is the type to be modified. For more complex implementations these methods can be overridden.

    • Method Detail

      • set

        default <A> TransactionResult set(Key<T,A> key,
                                  A appliedValue)
        Apply a given value of type A using a given Key type to the implementation of this interface. The type parameter of the value to apply, constrained by the type parameter of the given Key.
        Type Parameters:
        A - The type parameter of the applied value.
        Parameters:
        key - The key to apply, providing the constraints for the type to apply to and the type of the applied value.
        appliedValue - The applied value.
        Returns:
        The transaction result. If the transaction failed the TransactionResult will provide a message.

      • get

        default <A> Exceptional<A> get(Key<T,A> key)
        Retrieves a value from the implementation of this interface using a given Key. The Key provides the constraints for the returned type using type parameters A.
        Type Parameters:
        A - The type parameter of the returned value, constrained by the type parameter of the given Key.
        Parameters:
        key - The key to use when retrieving a value, providing the constraints for the returned value.
        Returns:
        The value wrapped in a Exceptional, which will contain a ClassCastException if this does not match the constraint of the given Key.
